<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Simple Log Filter</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <h1>Simple Log Filter for CE</h1>
    <p>Upload a log file. After parsing you can view ALL / INFO / DEBUG / ERROR logs (multiline preserved).</p>

    <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <input type="file" name="logfile" accept=".log,.txt" required />
      <button type="submit">Upload & Parse</button>
    </form>

    <section style="margin-top:18px;color:#666;font-size:0.95rem">
      <strong>Note:</strong> This demo stores parsed results in memory. For huge files, use DB or ES.
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
